summary: A creator explains their three-step process for passing a math exam. The steps involve making a list of topics to study, using an AI tool called Thetawise.ai to generate review videos for each topic, and doing practice questions until no mistakes are made.
transcript: My 3 step process to pass ANY math exam. 1. Make a list of all the topics you need to study. 2. Go to Thetawise.ai. Then ask the AI to generate a short video to review each topic. 3. Do practice questions until you literally don't get anything wrong. Repeat the last 2 steps per topic.
